Introduction

Thank you for using my software! This document is the main privacy policy for howlongtobeat. I respects your privacy rights and care about protecting your information collected by my app.


Security of Information:
Currently, no personal details are collected apart from login details, which is stored in an encrypted format in secure database.

No anonymous data is collected, without user's notice.

The code for the application is open source and is hosted on Github.
https://github.com/theTrivia/howlongtobeat


